{% extends "base.j2" %}

{% block title %}Home{% endblock %}

{% block extra_style %}
.hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #2c3e50, #1a252f);
    color: white;
    margin: -15px -15px 30px -15px;
}
.hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.hero p { font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 30px auto; opacity: 0.9; }

.cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--geo-red);
    color: white;
    padding: 18px 35px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(167, 0, 7, 0.4);
}

.mastery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin: 40px 0;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .mastery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

.transformation-box {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 30px;
    margin: 40px 0;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
}

.transform-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
}
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<section class="hero">
    <h1>Speak Without the Struggle.</h1>
    <p>Trade the grammar tables for muscle memory. Our drills turn complex Georgian rules into instant reflexes, so you can focus on the conversation, not the rules.</p>
    <a href="Verbs.html" class="cta-btn">Start Drilling Now — It's Free</a>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Stop Thinking, Start Feeling</h2>
    <p>Georgian grammar often feels like mental gymnastics. Look at: <strong>"The big dog saw me."</strong></p>

    <div class="transformation-box">
        <div class="transform-row"><strong>ძაღლი (Dog)</strong> <span style="color:var(--geo-red)">→</span> <strong>ძაღლმა</strong></div>
        <div class="transform-row"><strong>დიდი (Big)</strong> <span style="color:var(--geo-red)">→</span> <strong>დიდმა</strong></div>
        <div class="transform-row"><strong>ნახა (Saw)</strong> <span style="color:var(--geo-red)">→</span> <strong>მნახა</strong></div>
        <p style="margin-top:20px; font-style: italic; color: #555;">
            Native speakers don't calculate these endings—they intuit them. By drilling these specific shifts, you build the same muscle memory.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>The 3-Step Mastery System</h2>
    <div class="mastery-grid">
        <div class="card">
            <h4 style="margin-top:0">Level 1: Recognition</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">The "Warm Up." Train your brain to recognize the correct forms and sounds instantly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h4 style="margin-top:0">Level 2: Modification</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">The "Practice." Learn to manually shift base words into the correct forms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h4 style="margin-top:0">Level 3: Production</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">"Game Time." Produce the correct Georgian sentences from scratch with no hints.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section style="text-align:center; margin-top:60px;">
    <h2>50 GEL. Lifetime Access.</h2>
    <p>The first lesson of every module is free. Unlock the other 500+ specialized drills for a one-time payment.</p>
    <a href="Signup.html" class="cta-btn" style="background:var(--geo-dark)">Create Your Account</a>
</section>
{% endblock %}
